description:
Learn Arabic with ArabicPod101! No more dry, out of date textbook story lines! Here at ArabicPod101, you'll learn Arabic with fun, interesting and culturally relevant lessons that are easy to listen to. But not only are they fun - they're effective too! 

&quot;These podcasts offer a painless and FREE way to bone up on the language and culture in a relevant, real world way that you won't get in a class room or on a CDROM.&quot;
Brian Heater, PC Magazine
